        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 4. Comparison of mean spicule width and lengths (± 1 standard error) based on 20 measurements (for each specimen). Green symbols are Haliclona durdong sp. nov. and brown symbols are Haliclona djeedara sp. nov. square represent specimens from Jurien Bay, triangles are specimens from Rottnest Island, crosses are specimens from Hamelin Bay, and circles are specimens from Bremer Bay (see Table 1)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4921561/files/figure.png" .

